                                            </Run>
                                             - mechanics of the application that allows you to adjust
                                              the overall brightness of the computer monitor on which the program is running, and the volume
                                             system, through a bot
                                        </TextBlock>
                                        <TextBlock
                                            Foreground="White"
                                            TextWrapping="Wrap"
                                            Margin="10,15,0,0">
                                            <Run FontWeight="Bold" Foreground="{StaticResource telegramColor}">
                                               3. ScreenShot 
                                            </Run>
                                            - the ability of the program to take a screenshot: save it
                                             in the folder selected by the user and then send the result to the dialogue with the bot in Telegram
                                        </TextBlock>
